::Firearm/Rex/Kluster::

Firearm nods as he recieves Chordate's orders, looking at Rex. "Let's go."

The two set off toward the brig, carrying BrightBlade and Gangon with them.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Kluster closes the landing bay after the shuttle flies off. He really hoped 
those two knew what they were doing.

The commander of the Cybertronian Fire turns, walking out of the landing bay 
and off toward the bridge.
